scoringPlays.text: Nate Craig-Myers 6 Yd pass from Jarrett Stidham (Daniel Carlson Kick)
Isaac Nauta 2 Yd pass from Jake Fromm (Rodrigo Blankenship Kick)
Terry Godwin 7 Yd pass from Jake Fromm (Jake Fromm Pass to Terry Godwin for Two-Point Conversion)
D'Andre Swift 64 Yd Run (Rodrigo Blankenship Kick)

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham throws a laser into the end zone for Nate Craig-Myers who makes the catch to put Auburn up in the first quarter over Georgia.
videos.headline: Auburn scores first on Stidham's passing TD

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 11:30PM** NCF_One-Play (Auburn takes early lead on Stidham's passing TD) 2017/12/02 ESHEET

videos.description: The Bulldogs special teams comes up huge with a block on the field goal attempt for Auburn that would have tied the game in the 3rd quarter.
videos.headline: Georgia blocks Auburn's game-tying field goal attempt

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 11:30PM** NCF_One-Play (Georgia blocks Auburn's game-tying field goal attempt) 2017/12/02 ESHEET

videos.description: Georgia capitalizes on an Auburn fumble and Jake Fromm throws a touchdown to Terry Godwin and then the Bulldogs go up by 2 scores with the 2-point conversion.
videos.headline: Fromm tosses huge TD for Georgia, get 2-pt conv

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 11:30PM** NCF_One-Play (Fromm tosses huge TD for Georgia, get 2-pt conv) 2017/12/02 ESHEET

videos.description: D'Andre Swift finds the holes in the defense and takes off for a 64-yard touchdown to pad Georgia's lead in the SEC Championship game.
videos.headline: Swift blows by Auburn for 64-yard TD

tracking.trackingName: **UNPUB 11:30PM** NCF_One-Play (Swift blows by Auburn for 64-yard TD) 2017/12/02 ESHEET
